    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Portions of a whole, including subtances in the context of being combined with other substances, portions of temporal works, or portions of literary or dramatic works. For parts of visual works and other objects, prefer "components (object parts)."</Note_Text>
